             was indicted for <rs id="t17821204-9-off43" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821204-9-off43" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821204-9-off43" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17821204-9-cd44" type="crimeDate">30th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-9-off43 t17821204-9-cd44"></join> last ten pair of leather gloves, value 10 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17821204-9-victim134" type="victimName">Charles Langstone<interp inst="t17821204-9-victim134" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-9-off43 t17821204-9-victim134"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , privily in his shop
